title: Petra Matechová
text: Petra Matechová (born 8 December 1971) is a Czech <a href="luge">luge</a>r. She competed in the <a href="Luge%20at%20the%201992%20Winter%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20singles">women's singles event</a> at the <a href="1992%20Winter%20Olympics">1992 Winter Olympics</a>.
